Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.10,0:22:35.43,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}あぁ 朽ちていく世界ならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:39.00,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}散りゆく運命ならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.15,0:22:44.00,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}何を信じて生きればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:50.00,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}そう 君と出逢わなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:53.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}この胸を引き裂くような
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.96,0:22:59.63,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}痛みなんて知らなかったから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.96,0:23:04.33,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}空の彼方 鳴り響いた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.67,0:23:07.56,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}拙い鎮魂歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.67,0:23:07.56,ED,NTP,80,0,0,,{\be1\fs20}レクイエム
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.33,0:23:11.71,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}それでもまだ探している
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.18,0:23:14.80,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}不確かな現実から
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.18,0:23:14.80,ED,NTP,95,0,0,,{\be1\fs20}いま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.28,0:23:17.15,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}君のことを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.19,0:23:20.75,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}巡り逢えた歓びも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.89,0:23:24.48,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}消えていった温もりも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.63,0:23:28.73,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}ねぇ 全部覚えてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.00,0:23:31.77,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}愛してたから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:35.53,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}芽生えていく感情も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.73,0:23:39.30,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}胸に残る傷跡も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:43.45,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}ねぇ 全部抱えて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.78,0:23:50.38,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1}この道を歩いて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.10,0:22:35.43,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}倘若世界將要腐朽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:39.00,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}如果註定難逃死滅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.15,0:22:44.00,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}此生究竟該相信什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:50.00,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}是的 如果不曾與你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:53.70,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}我便不必體會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.96,0:22:59.63,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}這撕心裂肺的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.96,0:23:04.33,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}響徹在宇宙彼岸的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.67,0:23:07.56,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}是那稚拙的鎮魂之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.33,0:23:11.71,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.18,0:23:14.80,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}依然從飄乎的現實中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.28,0:23:17.15,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}找尋你的印記
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.19,0:23:20.75,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}相逢的喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.89,0:23:24.48,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}消散的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.63,0:23:28.73,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}我都歷歷在目
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.00,0:23:31.77,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}因為曾經深愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:35.53,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}萌生的情愫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.73,0:23:39.30,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}殘留的傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:43.45,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}我都銘記在心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.78,0:23:50.38,ED_CHT,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be1\an8}一路前行
Comment: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:19.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,=============STORY===============
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.26,0:00:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,袋狀結構破裂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.24,0:00:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探測不到任何奇居子的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,融合個體要不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認融合個體紬仍然存活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.88,0:00:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇居子剛才對我做了非常過分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.59,0:00:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能讓它們對我的朋友和同伴做那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.77,0:00:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬 希格斯粒子密度上升
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.50,0:00:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！紬！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:27.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬 聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科戶瀨機 嚴重損毀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.58,0:00:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇550的希格斯粒子密度急劇上升
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.39,0:00:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德尼婭！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.83,0:00:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,軌道在與紬和科戶瀨機的接觸點發生了變化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快來人 去救紬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.92,0:00:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬 紬她…！
Comment: 0,0:00:19.05,0:00:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（OP）
Comment: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:31.05,title,NTP,0,0,0,,願 望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,融合個體整備班 至岐神開發廠區特殊培養槽集合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.54,0:02:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船員醫療班 火速救治受傷的衛人操縱士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.90,0:02:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重傷者送往高度緊急治療室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輕傷者送往醫務局第三科或中央醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊札那！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.56,0:03:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們趕時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.03,0:03:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜 拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岐神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷風
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬 紬她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她現在喪失了90%的身體組織
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會把紬恢復原樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前出擊並回艦的機體中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.39,0:04:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前約有50%已完成整備並運回機庫待命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個融合個體又救了我們一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果沒有她 我們肯定已經無家可歸了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎瑪莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.87,0:04:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次真是好險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德尼婭和你都沒事真是萬幸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弦打——！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.79,0:05:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死性不改
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才打了那麼場惡戰啊 你就少計較點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過話說回來 沒想到你換成了義肢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是堅決啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是奶奶建議的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.91,0:05:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為組織再生要花很多時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手腳你很快就能適應的 不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還方便得很
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你挺精神的 我也放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候可以出院？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不說我了 長道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬還沒恢復嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&HC99DCF&}給紬姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&HC8A789&}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&HC8A789&}保護了希德尼婭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&H978FC9&}祝你能趕快好起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝她的人有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比之前好一些了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.03,0:07:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉換爐管的第1024次定期清掃將按時進行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本次清掃…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想快點向紬道謝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.46,0:07:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.27,0:07:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷風
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.57,0:07:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說戰鬥口糧換新了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去試吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…我就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那艘移民艦是在放出先遣隊後返航希德尼婭的途中遇襲的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能有人順利到達七號行星就已經不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是現在大眾合船正在逼近雷姆星系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.34,0:08:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就夠了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.18,0:08:09.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.81,0:08:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來很累的樣子 估計是沒怎麼睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷風他累了或者身體不舒服了也從來不說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.38,0:08:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得他的這一點很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.93,0:08:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也反而讓人擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前也認識一個和長道很像的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以常常很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在看到他一個人承擔太多東西的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是長道一定不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他一個人待一陣子 很快就會振作起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷風長道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天也來看望紬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.31,0:09:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嗯 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬已經移到通常培養槽了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胞衣已經基本上完全復原 只等恢復意識了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.77,0:09:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.94,0:09:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動了…！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她動了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.40,0:10:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你吃相太難看了啦 長道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？星…白…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷風
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星 白…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷風先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.25,0:11:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好…咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一不小心睡著了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看上去睡得很香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷 谷風先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紬！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊札那 你沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是多虧了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:11:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.71,0:12:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 聽說你醒了 我就把牠帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是貓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:12.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我可以摸摸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要溫柔一點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.17,0:12:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.26,0:12:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,軟軟的 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:28.01,eyecatch,NTP,1020,0,0,,希德尼婭百景　無人小攤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:30.98,eyecatch,NTP,950,0,0,,希德尼婭百景　外周壁連接橋內部通道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前希德尼婭與大眾合船所在的位置之間隔著恆星雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:44.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們處於對方的死角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.81,0:12:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為按照計劃進入雷姆星系 本艦將開始減速
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.19,0:12:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 繼續保持警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.94,0:12:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,融合個體的情況呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:13:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在為外殼設置了專用的房間 讓她在其中待命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現有武器再加上紬也還是敵不過大眾合船的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艦長是另有妙計嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經過上一場戰鬥 融合個體反對派的勢力已經大幅削弱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.66,0:13:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個東西怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就將進入第一次啟動實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:39.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫我轉告由蕾博士 我很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.99,0:13:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 能看到外面了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像比之前的房間大了一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:14:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡看書 所以小一點也沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谷風先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.06,0:14:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是覺得這裡離居住區有點遠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是沒辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 長道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從剛才開始就一聲不吭的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…我就是在剛才的紬身上看到了一個人住在地下的她的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 去拜託纈讓紬能夠進入居住區嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊 進來一下說不定還是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們說什麼傻話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來現在重力就已經不穩定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:14:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是發生事故怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們都給我差不多一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.70,0:15:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 別走那麼快啊 長道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是這個洞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 從管理局那邊拿到的地圖上也是這麼標的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 又是這麼黑漆漆的路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 出血了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起啊 長道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…我沒事 趕緊往前走吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德尼婭正面噴射口 已打開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓工作隊撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.94,0:16:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航向 行星九號的衛星軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.44,0:16:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備反向噴射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反向噴射準備
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.67,0:16:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發佈重力警報
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德尼婭現在將開始反向噴射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請將安全帶扣在安全扶手上 準備迎接衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希德尼婭現在將開始反向噴射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.11,0:16:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請將安全帶扣在安全扶手上 準備迎接衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長道 剛才是不是有什麼聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就差一點了 再加把勁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反向噴射 準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正面第一、第二噴射口 點火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始反向噴射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種振動是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 說起來今天是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噴射已穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重力場發生裝置及平衡即將恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要 要掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長道 到外面了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了 就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要開了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是居住塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.37,0:20:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那整棟建築裡住著很多人是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.24,0:20:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那裡有好多人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那麼多人 肯定也有很多種生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能變成人類的大小
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去很多地方 結識很多人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該有多棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們每個人都知道你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.36,0:20:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.93,0:20:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從來沒想過能親眼見到這樣的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:10.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的東西怎麼會在走廊上…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:20.67,*Default,NTP,150,0,0,,{\an7}谷風長道先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}今天是新訓練生入住的日子，
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}但是您的物品還未整理完畢。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}因此我們將其放到了門外。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}請見諒。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}希德尼婭軍總務科
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.20,0:21:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經不能再住宿舍了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.84,0:21:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我可不是在跟你說笑話啊 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.14,0:21:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.87,0:21:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你比計劃的要慢 所以我一直很擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 義肢也需要調整呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 有人來電了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.99,0:21:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 那我先掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 再見 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊札那？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.51,0:22:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長 長道 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 突然找你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.66,0:22:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.24,0:22:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天能讓我住一晚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.05,0:22:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.64,0:22:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒——？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.05,0:00:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（ED）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.10,0:24:26.98,title,NTP,0,0,0,,啟 動
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.22,0:24:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 啟動
